{"tid":635230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柒頭何君堯「殺無赦」言論　警方決定不起訴","createTime":"2018-04-20T03:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T09:28:29.000Z","uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c436693ba5535ff54b68da39b289d1ee4d74df24","tid":635230,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:24:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180419/bkn-20180419225508876-0419_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180419%2Fbkn-20180419225508876-0419_00822_001.html&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRANU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=210ff79c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180419/bkn-20180419225508876-0419_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n何君堯「殺無赦」言論　警方決定不起訴<br />\n<br />\n身為律師的立法會議員何君堯去年9月發起集會，要求香港大學開除違法佔中發起人、港大法律系副教授戴耀廷，期間何曾發表主張港獨者「殺無赦」的言論，有多名市民其後就「殺無赦」言論報警舉報，事隔7個月，據悉警方已完成調查，以證據不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為由決定不作起訴。<br />\n<br />\n另外，據報警方以電郵回覆一批報案舉報人士疑「甩轆」，未有以密件副本形式送出，令收到該封電郵的舉報人電郵地址曝光，據知有有200多人受事件影響。"},{"pid":"fb440c2fded72ecc9743cdcd5a26a779f15bd0cc","tid":635230,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df2a3c57c49a11513097fe8e4c589d81b3198c8","tid":635230,"uid":39277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"影撚住<br />\n<br />\n全香港咁多人睇新聞見證晒<br />\n<br />\n現場又幾百人係到都證據不足<br />\n<br />\n真係好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46326c8fe31a28d63c6e58c70ce5add6c11c6582","tid":635230,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f07f22f265d6410b380253233b1d9a124af250e","tid":635230,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime